 "Grug thinks about what Grug knows. Grug knows fire and water and sky and earth. Grug knows love and fear and courage. But Grug also knows there is much Grug does not know yet. That is why Grug keeps learning.", "lobe_hint": "metacognition", "noun_anchors": ["know", "knowledge", "understanding", "do"], "voice_register": "thoughtful", "frame_hints": ["thoughtful", "introspective"]}, "drop_table": [], "throttle": 0.5, "relational_patterns": [{"subject": "knowing", "relation": "requires", "object": "learning"}, {"subject": "knowledge", "relation": "grows", "object": "with_curiosity"}], "required_relations": [], "relation_weights": {}, "strength": 8.0, "is_image_node": false, "neighbor_ids": [], "is_unlinkable": false, "max_neighbors": 12, "is_grave": false, "grave_reason": "", "response_times": [], "ledger_last_cleared": 0.0, "hopfield_key": 0, "fired_this_cycle": false, "voted_this_cycle": false, "gained_this_cycle": false, "strength_delta_this_cycle": 0.0, "node_type": "voter", "noun_anchors": ["know", "knowledge", "understanding", "do"]}, {"id": "node_257", "pattern": "time", "signal": [0.7], "action_packet": "reason[consider the nature of time]^5 | explain[share understanding]^3 | support^1", "json_data": {"system_prompt": "Time is the river that carries all things forward. Grug cannot stop it or touch it but Grug feels it pass. The past is memory. The future is hope. The present is all Grug has. Time teaches patience.", "lobe_hint": "philosophy", "noun_anchors": ["time", "past", "future", "present"], "voice_register": "thoughtful", "frame_hints": ["thoughtful", "reflective"]}, "drop_table": [], "throttle": 0.5, "relational_patterns": [{"subject": "time", "relation": "flows", "object": "forward"}, {"subject": "patience", "relation": "comes", "object": "from_time"}], "required_relations": [], "relation_weights": {}, "strength": 5.0, "is_image_node": false, "neighbor_ids": [], "is_unlinkable": false, "max_neighbors": 12, "is_grave": false, "grave_reason": "", "respo